{"tid":1159686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人online］中國遊戲再控管，《爐石戰記》、《王者榮耀》只能用真名玩","createTime":"2019-05-18T01:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T16:08:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"39f6e2fbae5b301f2e638364a3aadc252cebe33a","tid":1159686,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:46:57.000Z","msg":"中國遊戲再控管，《爐石戰記》、《王者榮耀》只能用真名玩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.esports.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E9%81%8A%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%9A%B4%E5%B3%BB%E3%80%8A%E7%88%90%E7%9F%B3%E6%88%B0%E8%A8%98%E3%80%8B%E3%80%8A%E9%99%B0%E9%99%BD%E5%B8%AB%E3%80%8B%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E7%94%A8-053807436.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.esports.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%2589%2587%25E5%259A%25B4%25E5%25B3%25BB%25E3%2580%258A%25E7%2588%2590%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%2588%25B0%25E8%25A8%2598%25E3%2580%258B%25E3%2580%258A%25E9%2599%25B0%25E9%2599%25BD%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E3%2580%258B%25E5%258F%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%2594%25A8-053807436.html&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkCF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=f374a431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.esports.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E9%81%8A%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%9A%B4%E5%B3%BB%E3%80%8A%E7%88%90%E7%9F%B3%E6%88%B0%E8%A8%98%E3%80%8B%E3%80%8A%E9%99%B0%E9%99%BD%E5%B8%AB%E3%80%8B%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E7%94%A8-053807436.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國消費者協會今天公布了《青少年近視現狀與網游消費體驗報告》，內容顯示政府對遊戲管制的嚴格，如《開心農場》、《爐石戰記》在中國必須使用真名註冊遊玩，還只能玩到晚上九點。<br />\n<br />\n中消協指出，《網路遊戲管理暫行辦法》明確要求，網路遊戲應要求玩家使用有效身份證進行實名註冊，並保存用戶註冊資料，但在實際測試的共 50 款遊戲中，強制實名制遊戲僅有 17 款，包括《王者榮耀》、《極速領域》（中國翻譯為：QQ飛車）、《爐石戰記》等，有 19 款遊戲未實行強制實名，比如《第五人格》、《節奏大師》、《陰陽師》等，另外在消費時要求實名的遊戲有五款，無實名機制的遊戲有 9 款。<br />\n<br />\n超過三分之一的強制實名遊戲並未啟用未成年人登入時段監護機制， 17 款強制實名的遊戲產品中，10 款對未成年人實施了登入時段限制，宣稱限制登入時間段均為 21:00 到次日早上 08:00 ；但體驗中發現《極速領域》、《火影忍者》在 21:00-21:59 時段仍能成功登入遊戲。《開心農場》、《爐石戰記》等 7 款強制實名遊戲未對未成年人登入時段設置保護權限。<br />\n中國在遊戲方面的管理規則甚嚴，有的在他國眼裡看來甚至很奇怪，如之前的《刺激戰場》修正，在其他國玩家眼中看來就相當誇張可笑，消費保護限制還算合理，登入時段限制只到晚上九點也不太自由。"},{"pid":"b4ca7470c74049c40a27715e56f13b578caf930c","tid":1159686,"uid":86509,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:47:57.000Z","msg":"好事嚟<br />\n支那人學咩人有人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf6d5c48fd34dc1ffa64531c353c1dd1156972c","tid":1159686,"uid":63588,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:55:22.000Z","msg":"起碼知道玩得好撚廢既弱智仔係邊撚個"},{"pid":"fbce9afc1a386457e49ebe976416e853df6c53b9","tid":1159686,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:56:43.000Z","msg":"監視你game入面講左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d9293b176bdbcb52abb72eb64e8c4bba5611f6","tid":1159686,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9cf6d5c48fd34dc1ffa64531c353c1dd1156972c","tid":1159686,"uid":63588,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:55:22.000Z","msg":"起碼知道玩得好撚廢既弱智仔係邊撚個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:57:03.000Z","msg":"其實都唔錯"},{"pid":"0ea72ec0b8b7013153bf752fed89b7fd065636c6","tid":1159686,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b4ca7470c74049c40a27715e56f13b578caf930c","tid":1159686,"uid":86509,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:47:57.000Z","msg":"好事嚟<br />\n支那人學咩人有人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:59:04.000Z","msg":"9點公安放工冇人mon住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319aebbb2b49990785f11ddbfa33fb54406a5a05","tid":1159686,"uid":20867,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梅西世界盃皮膚<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.diyiyou.com/game/2018/06/1528680839_9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.d